channel.title: Champions
channel.desc: Wins 19 - 25. Black Caviar, Australia's sprinting champion race mare, trained by Peter Moody. Undefeated in 25 races including 15 Group 1 victories. Aust. Racehorse of the Year (2011, 2012, 2013), Aust. Champion Sprinter (2011, 2012, 2013).
